SUMMARY:Media School undergraduate spring commencement celebration
DESCRIPTION:We will recognize each graduate and hear from a student speak
 er and the dean. Graduating students were able to reserve up to 6 guest t
 ickets by May 1 (https://mediaschool.indiana.edu/news-events/commencement
 /index.html). Guests must have a ticket in order to attend the celebratio
 n.&#160\;  Find more details on the official IU commencement ceremonies (
 http://commencement.iu.edu/) for university-wide celebrations.  Dress is 
 business casual. For recognition ceremonies at IU Auditorium\, guests are
  permitted to bring clear bags (https://nam12.safelinks.protection.outloo
 k.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iuauditorium.com%2F&amp\;data=05%7C02%7Cdowe
 lla%40iu.edu%7C78ed62d7736342a3330e08dd52867c45%7C1113be34aed14d00ab4bcdd
